# Installation & Setup

## Clone the repository

```
git clone https://github.com/your-username/call-analytics-dashboard.git
```

```
cd call-analytics-dashboard
```

---

## Install dependencies

```
npm install
```

---

## Run development server

```
npm run dev
```

---

## Build for production

```
npm run build
```

